==特色==
[[Image:All_That_Remains_live_in_East_Troy_at_Ozzfest_2006.jpg|thumb]] performing at the [[Ozzfest|Ozzfest]] in 2006.]]
旋律金属核深受吉他[[riff|riff]]和[[瑞典旋律死亡金属|瑞典旋律死亡金属]]乐队作曲风格，尤其是[[At_the_Gates|At the Gates]]，<ref name="amg">{{cite web |author=D. Taylor, Jason |url={{Allmusic|class=album|id=suicide-notes-and-butterfly-kisses-mw0000223292|pure_url=yes}} |title=''Suicide Notes and Butterfly Kisses'' review |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |accessdate=June 24, 2008 |quote=Atreyu's debut album, Suicide Notes and Butterfly Kisses, is an invigorating foray into melodic metalcore in the vein of Darkest Hour, Poison the Well, and Eighteen Visions.}}</ref> [[邪神大敌|邪神大敌]]，[[烈焰邪神|烈焰邪神]]和[[撒旦之作乐团|撒旦之作乐团]]的影响，他们在自己的作品中运用大量的器乐[[旋律|旋律]]。许多旋律金属核常常是清嗓与嘶吼共存。还有泛音吉他[[riff|riff]]，[[交替上下拨弦|交替上下拨弦]],[[大鼓#Double_bass|双踩]]和金属风格的[[分解联奏|breakdown]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://media.www.elpaisanonewspaper.com/media/storage/paper1088/news/2007/09/12/Entertainment/Its-Through.The.Approach-2961653.shtml |title=It's Through the Approach |work=El Paisano |date=September 12, 2007 |accessdate=June 24, 2008 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090114065351/http://media.www.elpaisanonewspaper.com/media/storage/paper1088/news/2007/09/12/Entertainment/Its-Through.The.Approach-2961653.shtml |archivedate=2009年1月14日 |df= }}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref>


